title: Statement regarding allegations tabled to Queensland Parliament (Tablelands Regional Council)
text: ( Source : Tablelands Regional Council ) Tablelands Regional Council Mayor Rosa Lee Long and Chief Executive Officer Ian Church strongly refute the allegations outlined in a document tabled by Rob Pyne , Member for Cairns today in Queensland
